{"tid":1661731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民主女神之人血饅頭","createTime":"2019-10-18T09:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:09:41.000Z","uid":293547,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d2261ed07e15ff681ed17f898825771ea4a80aab","tid":1661731,"uid":293547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"昨日，我開ＦＢ睇下玩具ＧＰ，睇到有個賣３Ｄ　Ｐｒｉｎｔ　ＧＥ友仔話代印女神，係佢。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMG2qep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMG2qep.jpg&h=fb28e6b6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n哈哈。。。　我當堂嚇一跳，然後得啖笑。呢個香港，居然有人咁樣搵食，咁即係分明食人血饅頭唧！<br />\n我就即刻ＰＭ佢，問佢咩價位。。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkXUgnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkXUgnP.jpg&h=3ae0e0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/foULn2T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfoULn2T.jpg&h=6e2df8b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩，１４ＣＭ高　（０。２　Ｌａｙｅｒ　Ｈｅｉｇｈｔ）賣８９９！？！？！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nＦＵＬＬ　ＳＥＴ　＄１９９０仲有旗仔送咁貼心！？！？<br />\n睇到哩度，作為一個精明消費者，當然唔想被消費啦，立即就繼續扮下有興趣，問下佢會捐幾多俾星火！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WKO5if.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WKO5if.jpg&h=d517f61b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n５&mdash;１０％？有Ｄ人仲會俾多Ｄ叫佢捐！？！？！？！？！？！？！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有好多單！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好喇，講到哩度，可能你會問，點解我咁肯定係人血饅頭呢？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1tsBvp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1tsBvp.jpg&h=f0595028&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24DguQw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24DguQw.jpg&h=41903f2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為我都ＰＲＩＮＴ左幾隻１６ＣＭ高（比佢提供ＧＥ　ＳＩＺＥ再大少少）ＬＡＹＥＲ佢用０。２，我用０。０３（我冇打多個０呀），如圖中所見，ＰＲＩＮＴ一隻１６ＣＭ高大約用左４４粒鐘。就以１６ＣＭ為例，咁到底成本係幾多呢？１Ｌ　ＲＥＳＩＮ大約６００蚊，以１６ＣＭ黎計大約ＰＲＩＮＴ到５隻，計埋電費，２００蚊都應該唔洗。計埋事前拎張圖加下ＳＵＰＰＯＲＴＩＮＧ（一次性），ＰＲＩＮＴ完又浸洗下火酒哩Ｄ程序，就當你成本３００蚊啦。一隻賺６００蚊，捐５&mdash;１０％俾星火，賣價５０％利潤就咁落左自己袋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲未計如果ＦＵＬＬ　ＳＥＴ會賺更多（因為有可能都係ＰＲＩＮＴ一轉就ＰＲＩＮＴ到晒４個ＳＩＺＥ）<br />\n多個人睇到，少個人中招，大家一齊幫下佢手啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed73e46b5aa207505a524ba980c766dbf78ac48","tid":1661731,"uid":16367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"28fb30e5213c228238857afdfd76861b866535e9","tid":1661731,"uid":73248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f37a2600461050a82df1968546964c27014f1f3","tid":1661731,"uid":6140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:46:26.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 食人血饅頭正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd6f098df32841d65e6f84a382b8aa768b9d4a4","tid":1661731,"uid":74598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭仆街死"},{"pid":"e4d1886464cd547ce3f9016153adb042d0cbc43a","tid":1661731,"uid":266668,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"5-10%都夠膽死講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c426c8f73aa3d46f265018d283a057ec7567b2b6","tid":1661731,"uid":96406,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"鴻福郎再世？"},{"pid":"